tags.description: Gədəbəy (also, Gädäbäy, Gadabay, Kedabek, Kedabeko, Kedalek, Gedabek and Kyadabek) is a city in and capital of the Gadabay Rayon of Azerbaijan.

tags.description: Sarıhəsənli (also, Sarygasanli) is a village in the Gadabay Rayon of Azerbaijan. The village forms part of the municipality of Şəkərbəy.
